<body>
    <h1>Preconditions</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>This section describes the expected state of Ascension Health Al=
liance=E2=80=99s existing IAM platform for the <strong>Voyager </strong>pro=
gram. Requirements and design for the Voyager program will be created based=
 on the current state of the IAM platform.</p>
<p>Table-4</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1038" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"7=
04b4d31-1448-40d1-a8d7-671f51fb8abb" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 67.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 970.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>S.no.</strong></p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Precondition</strong></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Availability of working Development, SIT and UAT IAM environments with c=
ode replica of current production environment. The required level of access=
 to these systems are granted to the project team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>All available Active Directory domains are integrated with the current I=
AM platform with required configuration for account and access management w=
ith attribute synchronization.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Account and access management for ServiceNow application is already conf=
igured in the existing IAM platform and working without existing issues.</p=
></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>ServiceNow ServiceDesk integration is already in place in the existing I=
AM platform to manage ServiceNow ticket creation from the IAM platform.</p>=
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>5</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>PeopleSoft is the existing authoritative source integrated with the curr=
ent IAM platform for user data.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>6</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The existing IAM platform is already managing users accounts and access =
for GSuite application.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>7</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ascension Health Alliance=E2=80=99s existing OIM platform receives a fee=
d file with user data from Oracle PeopleSoft application.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
    </div>
</body>
